[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":1737},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fother\u002F20220211\u002F2705866340\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fother\u002F20220211\u002F2705866340\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fother\u002F20220211\u002F2705866340\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fother\u002F20220211\u002F2705866340\u002F":1713,"related:\u002Fother\u002F20220211\u002F2705866340\u002F":1722},"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2022\u002F02\u002F11\u002Fgoogle-apps-script-sheets-as-rest-api\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":1698,"date":1699,"description":18,"extension":1700,"lang":1701,"meta":1702,"navigation":1323,"path":1703,"readingMinutes":1704,"seo":1705,"standalone":1706,"stem":1707,"tags":1708,"tldr":1710,"updated":1710,"url":1711,"__hash__":1712},"content\u002F雜談\u002F用-Google-Apps-Script-搭配-Google-試算表開一個-API.md","用 Google Apps Script 搭配 Google 試算表開一個 API","2705866340",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":1684},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,29,32,41,44,50,59,62,65,71,74,80,83,89,97,101,104,110,113,118,126,132,136,139,143,150,196,202,205,209,222,269,279,285,296,303,339,342,347,350,356,360,363,369,372,378,381,387,390,396,400,403,406,477,480,541,547,554,628,637,643,649,725,728,733,736,740,747,769,785,797,857,868,960,963,967,970,976,979,985,988,994,997,1003,1006,1012,1015,1021,1031,1146,1149,1155,1158,1163,1166,1172,1176,1179,1275,1278,1581,1584,1654,1657,1660,1680],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"有時候我們會臨時需要開一個 API 來用，但是卻又不想自己開一個後端，例如像是 Koa、Express 或是 Laravel 等等框架，因為實在太麻煩，因此這時候就可以使用 Google Apps Script 服務來達到這個需求，其中也可以用 Google Apps Script 串接 Google 試算表，將 Google 試算表當作資料庫來使用。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"google-apps-script","Google Apps Script",[16,24,25],{},[26,27],"img",{"alt":22,"src":28},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-apps-script\u002F1J6Qm1Gr3RaG1oVPW5v4-0Q.png",[16,30,31],{},"首先 Google Apps Script 是什麼呢？Google Apps Script 是 Google 所開發的腳本平台，非常地輕量，起源主要是協助 Google 試算表輔助開發平台，因此 Google Apps Script 非常適合用來串接 Google 試算表，而 Google Apps Script 也非常類似小型的後端伺服器，因此也可以做一些處理。",[16,33,34,35,40],{},"當然在前面的封面圖中，如果你有認真看你會發現 Google Apps Script 做的事情非常多，例如我先前有寫過一篇文章是「",[36,37,39],"a",{"href":38},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20190617\u002F3829122039\u002F","使用 Google Apps Script 解決 CORS 問題","」，但這一篇我們就專注於串接 Google 試算表就好。",[16,42,43],{},"除此之外 Google Apps Script 的學習成本也相當低，尤其是對於一個 JavaScript 工程師來講會更親民，因為主要語法都是採用網頁程式語言，也就是 CSS、HTML 與 JavaScript 撰寫",[16,45,46],{},[26,47],{"alt":48,"src":49},"使用常用的網頁程式語言","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-apps-script\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-02-11%2009.57.22.png",[16,51,52,53,58],{},"那麼接下來就讓我們試著去撰寫 ",[36,54,22],{"href":55,"rel":56},"https:\u002F\u002Fworkspace.google.com\u002Fintl\u002Fzh-TW\u002Fproducts\u002Fapps-script\u002F",[57],"nofollow"," 吧。",[12,60,61],{"id":61},"建立試算表",[16,63,64],{},"一開始我想先請你試著建立一個 Google 試算表，打開 Google 雲端硬碟，右鍵選擇「Google」 試算表",[16,66,67],{},[26,68],{"alt":69,"src":70},"Google 試算表","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-apps-script\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-02-11%2010.00.03.png",[16,72,73],{},"建立成功後標題你可以在右上角改一下，讓自己好辨識一下",[16,75,76],{},[26,77],{"alt":78,"src":79},"重新命名","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-apps-script\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-02-11%2010.01.15.png",[16,81,82],{},"而內容你可以參考我的內容或者你自己打也可以",[16,84,85],{},[26,86],{"alt":87,"src":88},"試算表內容","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-apps-script\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-02-11%2010.06.31.png",[16,90,91,92,96],{},"最後這邊紀錄一下試算表的 Url，等一下你會用到，例如：",[36,93,94],{"href":94,"rel":95},"https:\u002F\u002Fdocs.google.com\u002Fspreadsheets\u002Fd\u002F1MQPaKCV446eLXg2mDlLeKpsMc4nRnHDC7swlijAzkz0\u002Fedit#gid=0",[57]," (該試算表連結只是示範而已)。",[12,98,100],{"id":99},"建立-google-apps-script","建立 Google Apps Script",[16,102,103],{},"首先回到 Google 雲端硬碟中建立一個 Google Apps Script，它的位置通常在「更多」裡面",[16,105,106],{},[26,107],{"alt":108,"src":109},"Google Apps Script 建立","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-apps-script\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96_2022-02-11_10_09_21.png",[16,111,112],{},"名稱你也可以點一下上方重新命名一下，不然到時候你會找不到 QQ",[16,114,115],{},[26,116],{"alt":78,"src":117},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-apps-script\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-02-11%2010.14.37.png",[16,119,120,121,125],{},"接下來在下方畫面上你可以看到一個 ",[122,123,124],"code",{},"myFunction"," 的初始地方，該處就是我們準備撰寫成程式碼的地方",[16,127,128],{},[26,129],{"alt":130,"src":131},"初始化","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-apps-script\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-02-11%2010.15.22.png",[12,133,135],{"id":134},"google-apps-script-起手式","Google Apps Script 起手式",[16,137,138],{},"那麼我們該如何起手呢？其實就如同前面所言，Google Apps Script 採用的是網頁程式語言所撰寫",[16,140,141],{},[26,142],{"alt":48,"src":49},[16,144,145,146,149],{},"你可以在裡面像寫 JavaScript 一樣宣告變數、",[122,147,148],{},"console.log"," 輸出都可以",[151,152,157],"pre",{"className":153,"code":154,"language":155,"meta":156,"style":156},"language-js shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","const myName = 'Ray';\nconsole.log(myName);\n","js","",[122,158,159,183],{"__ignoreMap":156},[160,161,164,168,172,175,179],"span",{"class":162,"line":163},"line",1,[160,165,167],{"class":166},"sWyjQ","const",[160,169,171],{"class":170},"sCcAr"," myName",[160,173,174],{"class":166}," =",[160,176,178],{"class":177},"sTRMh"," 'Ray'",[160,180,182],{"class":181},"sMAXC",";\n",[160,184,186,189,193],{"class":162,"line":185},2,[160,187,188],{"class":181},"console.",[160,190,192],{"class":191},"sj_SG","log",[160,194,195],{"class":181},"(myName);\n",[16,197,198],{},[26,199],{"alt":200,"src":201},"撰寫 Apps Script","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-apps-script\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-02-11%2010.19.21.png",[16,203,204],{},"因此完全不用太擔心我們還要額外學什麼，接下來就直接進入正題，也就是搭配 Google 試算表開一個 API。",[12,206,208],{"id":207},"連接特定-google-試算表","連接特定 Google 試算表",[16,210,211,212,215,216,221],{},"那麼在 Google Apps Script 中有提供一個方法可以讓你開啟特定 Google 試算表，也就是 ",[122,213,214],{},"SpreadsheetApp.openById"," 語法，你可以透過這個",[36,217,220],{"href":218,"rel":219},"https:\u002F\u002Fdevelopers.google.com\u002Fapps-script\u002Freference\u002Fspreadsheet\u002Fspreadsheet-app#openById(String)",[57],"連結","看到官方所提供的範例",[151,223,225],{"className":153,"code":224,"language":155,"meta":156,"style":156},"var ss = SpreadsheetApp.openById(\"abc1234567\");\nLogger.log(ss.getName());\n",[122,226,227,253],{"__ignoreMap":156},[160,228,229,232,235,238,241,244,247,250],{"class":162,"line":163},[160,230,231],{"class":166},"var",[160,233,234],{"class":181}," ss ",[160,236,237],{"class":166},"=",[160,239,240],{"class":181}," SpreadsheetApp.",[160,242,243],{"class":191},"openById",[160,245,246],{"class":181},"(",[160,248,249],{"class":177},"\"abc1234567\"",[160,251,252],{"class":181},");\n",[160,254,255,258,260,263,266],{"class":162,"line":185},[160,256,257],{"class":181},"Logger.",[160,259,192],{"class":191},[160,261,262],{"class":181},"(ss.",[160,264,265],{"class":191},"getName",[160,267,268],{"class":181},"());\n",[16,270,271,272,275,276,278],{},"(附註：Google Apps Script 中大多都是用 ",[122,273,274],{},"Logger.log"," 語法，如果你想用 ",[122,277,148],{}," 也可以，這兩者語法都有支援。)",[16,280,281,282,284],{},"那麼 ",[122,283,243],{}," 我們要傳入什麼呢？也就是我們要開啟的試算表 ID，因此這邊就會需要剛剛我們建立的 Google 試算表 Url",[151,286,290],{"className":287,"code":288,"language":289,"meta":156,"style":156},"language-txt shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","https:\u002F\u002Fdocs.google.com\u002Fspreadsheets\u002Fd\u002F1MQPaKCV446eLXg2mDlLeKpsMc4nRnHDC7swlijAzkz0\u002Fedit#gid=0\n","txt",[122,291,292],{"__ignoreMap":156},[160,293,294],{"class":162,"line":163},[160,295,288],{},[16,297,298,299,302],{},"裡面有一段 ",[122,300,301],{},"1MQPaKCV446eLXg2mDlLeKpsMc4nRnHDC7swlijAzkz0"," 這個就是我們要的試算表 ID",[151,304,306],{"className":153,"code":305,"language":155,"meta":156,"style":156},"var ss = SpreadsheetApp.openById(\"1MQPaKCV446eLXg2mDlLeKpsMc4nRnHDC7swlijAzkz0\");\nLogger.log(ss.getName());\n",[122,307,308,327],{"__ignoreMap":156},[160,309,310,312,314,316,318,320,322,325],{"class":162,"line":163},[160,311,231],{"class":166},[160,313,234],{"class":181},[160,315,237],{"class":166},[160,317,240],{"class":181},[160,319,243],{"class":191},[160,321,246],{"class":181},[160,323,324],{"class":177},"\"1MQPaKCV446eLXg2mDlLeKpsMc4nRnHDC7swlijAzkz0\"",[160,326,252],{"class":181},[160,328,329,331,333,335,337],{"class":162,"line":185},[160,330,257],{"class":181},[160,332,192],{"class":191},[160,334,262],{"class":181},[160,336,265],{"class":191},[160,338,268],{"class":181},[16,340,341],{},"這樣子你就可以取得我們剛剛的 Google 試算表，你可以試著將它貼入到 Google Apps Script 中",[16,343,344],{},[26,345],{"alt":22,"src":346},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-apps-script\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-02-11%2010.32.06.png",[16,348,349],{},"接下來就可以來按一下上方執行按鈕囉",[16,351,352],{},[26,353],{"alt":354,"src":355},"執行","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-apps-script\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-02-11%2010.33.26.png",[12,357,359],{"id":358},"初次執行-google-apps-script-的狀況","初次執行 Google Apps Script 的狀況",[16,361,362],{},"第一次執行這個 Google Apps Script 時你會跳出一個審查權限的畫面，不用怕按下審查權限",[16,364,365],{},[26,366],{"alt":367,"src":368},"審查權限","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-apps-script\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-02-11%2010.34.03.png",[16,370,371],{},"接下來選擇自己當前使用的帳號",[16,373,374],{},[26,375],{"alt":376,"src":377},"使用帳號","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-apps-script\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96_2022-02-11_10_34_11.png",[16,379,380],{},"最後你必須允許你當前的 Google Apps Script 檔案有權限去讀取試算表，否則你會無法使用",[16,382,383],{},[26,384],{"alt":385,"src":386},"允許","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fgoogle-apps-script\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96_2022-02-11_10_34_27.png",[16,38